donor_name: UNDP AS ADMINISTRATIVE AGENT FOR A JOINT PROGRAMME PASS THROUGH ARRANGEMENT
outputs.output_descr: International UNVs specialists are placed in District Social Welfare Offices (Technical Advisers) and at the Ministry's headquarters (Information Technical specialists) to ensure quality implementation of the OVC programme activities & for building capacity at District Social Welfare level to safeguard continuity and sustainability; and to assist establish a national OVC electronic management information system at the Ministry respectively.
